HEADWORD: Holstein-Friesian
<hw>Holstein-Friesian</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A breed of dairy cattle
from North Holland and Friesland; they have a black and white color to
their fur.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Friesian, Holstein.</syn>⟦br⟧
